snippet.title: Cat Leather Jackets | Teaser
snippet.description:
Cat Leather Jackets is a music game/ visual novel hybrid about a teenage punk rock band. Follow Priya and her friends as they write, rehearse and perform songs, all the while dealing with the frustrations and drama of being young and trying to figure out what life is all about.

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1673830/Cat_Leather_Jackets/

Cat Leather Jackets is co-developed by diogoh3x and Garoa Studios!

Follow diogoh3x: https://twitter.com/diogoh3x
Follow Garoa Studios on all platforms: https://linktr.ee/garoastudios
